        "description": "<p>Simple GDPR Cookie Compliance is a simple plugin that helps to display cookie notice on your WordPress website. It helps to show your complies with EU GDPR cookie law and CCPA regulations. It is a lightweight plugin that comes with three different layouts.<\/p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><em>Simple yet powerful plugin. Display cookie notice with just in few clicks. Adds just 2KB of pure vanilla JavaScript!<\/em><\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n<p>\ud83d\udc81 Note: Installing this plugin alone does not make your site GDPR compliant. Since each site uses different cookies, you may need to ensure you have necessary configurations in place.<\/p>\n<h3>\ud83e\udd84 Main Features<\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Simple &amp; light-weight.<\/li>\n<li>Three different layouts.<\/li>\n<li>Choose placement to display notice.<\/li>\n<li>Custom message support.<\/li>\n<li>Color options for notice.<\/li>\n<li>Display\/Hide close button.<\/li>\n<li>Display\/Hide cookie icon.<\/li>\n<li>Set cookie expiration date.<\/li>\n<li>Translation ready.<\/li>\n<li>Coded according to WordPress plugin standard.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3>\ud83c\udfad Get Involved<\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>If you&#8217;re a developer and want to contribute, you can do on <a href=\"https:\/\/github.com\/themebeez\/simple-gdpr-cookie-compliance\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Github<\/a>.<\/li>\n<li>If you love this plugin, and you want the plugin to be translated in your local language. Feel free to contribute on this <a href=\"https:\/\/translate.wordpress.org\/projects\/wp-plugins\/simple-gdpr-cookie-compliance\/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">translation page<\/a> for translation.<\/li>\n<li>If you&#8217;re a user and you need support or find any issues related to the plugin, please raise it on <a href=\"https:\/\/github.com\/themebeez\/simple-gdpr-cookie-compliance\/issues\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Github<\/a> or post it on <a href=\"https:\/\/themebeez.com\/support-forum\/simple-gdpr-cookie-compliance-support\/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">our support forum.<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3>\ud83d\udcb0 Financial Contributors &amp; Sponsors<\/h3>\n<p>Following are the list of financial contributors &amp; sponsors who have contributed to this plugin.<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http:\/\/www.zadarko.hr\/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Darko Pe\u010danac<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Become a financial contributor\/sponsor and help us sustain Simple GDPR Cookie Compliance plugin. Interested?  Contact us to <a href=\"https:\/\/creamcode.org\/contact\/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Contribute<\/a>.<\/p>\n<h3>Important Links<\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Source code &#8211; <a href=\"https:\/\/github.com\/themebeez\/simple-gdpr-cookie-compliance\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Github<\/a><\/li>\n<li>Feedback &#8211; <a href=\"https:\/\/wordpress.org\/support\/plugin\/simple-gdpr-cookie-compliance\/reviews\/\" rel=\"ugc\">Here<\/a><\/li>\n<li>Report an issue &#8211; <a href=\"https:\/\/themebeez.com\/support-forum\/simple-gdpr-cookie-compliance-support\/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Here<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n",
        "installation": "<ul>\n<li>On your dashboard, navigate to Plugins<\/li>\n<li>Click on Add New button<\/li>\n<li>On search field, type &#8220;Simple GDPR Cookie Compliance&#8221;<\/li>\n<li>Once you find the plugin, click on Install Now button<\/li>\n<li>After successful installation of the plugin, click on Activate button to activate plugin<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n",
        "faq": "\n<dt id='is%20this%20a%20free%20plugin%3F'>\nIs this a free plugin?\n<\/h4>\n<p>\n<p>Yes, it is. Simple GDPR Cookie Compliance will remain free forever.<\/p>\n<\/p>\n<dt id='how%20do%20i%20customize%20my%20message%3F'>\nHow do I customize my message?\n<\/h4>\n<p>\n<p>Click on Simple GDPR on your dashboard. It will lead you to the plugin&#8217;s page where you can find options to customize your message.<\/p>\n<\/p>\n<dt id='do%20you%20provide%20free%20support%3F'>\nDo you provide free support?\n<\/h4>\n<p>\n<p>Yes, we do. Kindly visit us at <a href=\"https:\/\/themebeez.com\/support-forum\/simple-gdpr-cookie-compliance-support\/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">support page<\/a> &amp; ask for support.<\/p>\n<\/p>\n\n",
        "changelog": "<h4>1.1.7 &#8211; 03 November, 2023<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tested: WordPress version 6.4.0<\/li>\n<li>Updated: Readme.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.1.6 &#8211; 14 August, 2023<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tested: WordPress version 6.3.0<\/li>\n<li>Updated: POT file.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.1.5 &#8211; 21 April, 2023<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: Wrong cookie path while accepting cookie notice #43<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.1.4 &#8211; 21 March, 2023<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tweak: Public custom JavaScript. Converted jQuery code to vanilla JavaScript.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.1.3 &#8211; 07 March, 2023<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Update: Static texts in UDP Agents are now translation ready.<\/li>\n<li>Update: WPCS implemented.<\/li>\n<li>Fix: Minor PHP error.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.1.2 &#8211; 03 March, 2023<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Updated: UDP agent to version 1.0.1.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.1.1 &#8211; 20 February, 2023<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added: Basic CSS style for the notice overlay.<\/li>\n<li>Added: UDP agent support.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.1.0 &#8211; 31 August, 2022<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tested: with WordPress version 6.0.2.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0.9 &#8211; 11 August, 2022<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: Session Cookie issue fixed.<\/li>\n<li>Added: Multisite support.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0.8 &#8211; 23 January, 2022<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tested: WordPress version 5.9<\/li>\n<li>Tested: PHP version 7.4<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0.7 &#8211; July 20, 2021<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: Minor PHP issues<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0.6 &#8211; July 20, 2021<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tested: up to WordPress 5.8<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0.5 &#8211; Feb 19, 2021<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: Setting page link<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0.4 &#8211; Dec 17, 2020<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added: Options customization options.<\/li>\n<li>Fix: Other minor issues<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0.3 &#8211; August 13, 2020<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Testing: Tested on WordPress version 5.5<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0.2 &#8211; 1 December, 2019<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added: Link type options<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0.1 &#8211; 4 November, 2019<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added: Color options<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0.0 &#8211; 2 August, 2019<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial release<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n",
        "screenshots": "<ol><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/simple-gdpr-cookie-compliance\/assets\/screenshot-1.png?rev=2778058\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/simple-gdpr-cookie-compliance\/assets\/screenshot-1.png?rev=2778058\" alt=\"Simple GDPR cookie compliance plugin at dashboard.\"><\/a><p>Simple GDPR cookie compliance plugin at dashboard.<\/p><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/simple-gdpr-cookie-compliance\/assets\/screenshot-2.png?rev=2778058\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/simple-gdpr-cookie-compliance\/assets\/screenshot-2.png?rev=2778058\" alt=\"Simple GDPR cookie compliance plugin page at dashboard.\"><\/a><p>Simple GDPR cookie compliance plugin page at dashboard.<\/p><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/simple-gdpr-cookie-compliance\/assets\/screenshot-3.png?rev=2778058\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/simple-gdpr-cookie-compliance\/assets\/screenshot-3.png?rev=2778058\" alt=\"Simple GDPR cookie compliance plugin at dashboard.\"><\/a><p>Simple GDPR cookie compliance plugin at dashboard.<\/p><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/simple-gdpr-cookie-compliance\/assets\/screenshot-4.png?rev=2867952\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/simple-gdpr-cookie-compliance\/assets\/screenshot-4.png?rev=2867952\" alt=\"Simple GDPR cookie compliance default notice.\"><\/a><p>Simple GDPR cookie compliance default notice.<\/p><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/simple-gdpr-cookie-compliance\/assets\/screenshot-5.png?rev=2867952\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/simple-gdpr-cookie-compliance\/assets\/screenshot-5.png?rev=2867952\" alt=\"Simple GDPR cookie compliance default notice layout 2.\"><\/a><p>Simple GDPR cookie compliance default notice layout 2.<\/p><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/simple-gdpr-cookie-compliance\/assets\/screenshot-6.png?rev=2867952\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/simple-gdpr-cookie-compliance\/assets\/screenshot-6.png?rev=2867952\" alt=\"Simple GDPR cookie compliance default notice layout 3.\"><\/a><p>Simple GDPR cookie compliance default notice layout 3.<\/p><\/li><\/ol>",
        "reviews": "<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Fast and simple, but not support more lanuages<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"4 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"4\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/stieranka\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/2adfd3b10c2ebcc9b0a8888a8bb0051b?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/2adfd3b10c2ebcc9b0a8888a8bb0051b?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/stieranka\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">stieranka<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 14, 2024<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Perfect plugin for GDPR, simple and verry fast, but it does not support multilingual display. I hope they will add it in the next versions. <\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">But I definitely recommend it!<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">best simple plugin<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/rozhko\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/f4e5a1856e5bb25e6133ebb0dd00438d?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/f4e5a1856e5bb25e6133ebb0dd00438d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/rozhko\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">rozhko<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">May 2, 2023<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>best simple plugin. no bootstrap, no jQuery. 1.4 kb js and css only.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Simple and practical<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/hoomanik\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/a42ee025a36e8d895f389128a446cf29?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/a42ee025a36e8d895f389128a446cf29?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/hoomanik\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">hoomanik<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 22, 2023<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Finally what I was looking for. A free simple plugin, with just an accept button.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Unfortunately it depends on jQuery<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/leninzapata\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/980a26eab7c4dd3fd8d33eecaa3fe8e0?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/980a26eab7c4dd3fd8d33eecaa3fe8e0?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/leninzapata\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Lenin Zapata <small>(leninzapata)<\/small><\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 22, 2023<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The plugin is lightweight and does its job, but you can't say it's really lightweight if your code line depends on jQuery which is considered too heavy a library. You should use native vanilla Javascript, not jQuery. There are Themes and Plugins that do not depend on jQuery in order not to alter the performance of the website. This is not the case.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Update:<\/strong> The author stopped relying on jQuery code, replaced it with the native one which makes the website more optimal.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great plugin<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/cristiano\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/2bf8f344c1f0f05d3cc695bcabacb03a?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/2bf8f344c1f0f05d3cc695bcabacb03a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/cristiano\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Cristiano <small>(cristiano)<\/small><\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 18, 2023<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We\u2019ve been using it fou couple of monthly now and we\u2019re satisfied!<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Thanks for simplifying!<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/ribeiroeder\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/707c37774849440400810360a4e7d07e?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/707c37774849440400810360a4e7d07e?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/ribeiroeder\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Eder Ribeiro <small>(ribeiroeder)<\/small><\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 11, 2023<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I must have tested about 10 different plugins, always with exaggerated, complicated, unnecessary options and in order to sell a paid plan.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In this plugin I could find everything I need: customize colors, messages and notification positions. Simple and functional.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Thanks!!<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Just have a cookie acceptance on the homepage<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/gg883\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/db8cb4aa53bc203593fdf648b7859e3d?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/db8cb4aa53bc203593fdf648b7859e3d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/gg883\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">gg883<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 7, 2023<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Thanks for your plugin .<br \/>I allow myself a remark, there would be the possibility that the message is displayed only once on the home page and not some of the other pages visited, as is practically the case.<br \/>You will have the opportunity to see this when you go there.<br \/>Waiting for your return<br \/>Thanks by advance<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Regards<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Doesn&#039;t work<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/nataliaszw\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/5706ff080c61dd28539d17e6339db52a?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/5706ff080c61dd28539d17e6339db52a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/nataliaszw\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Natalia <small>(NataliaSzw)<\/small><\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">June 14, 2022<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">Doesn't work<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Finally a lightweight cookie plugin<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/tezalsec\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/6fff7999331de37636be6ae7f2db4a8a?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/6fff7999331de37636be6ae7f2db4a8a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/tezalsec\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">tezalsec<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 20, 2022<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">First review! \n\nThank you for this lightweight plugin! Many of the most used cookie plugins have become so heavy, bloated and complex, this is like a breath of fresh air.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n"
